{
  "stem": "8370.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, they are coming to the camp, have been sent people from all around Europe, with instruments even, with violin, with trombones and clarinets and everything.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they had a chance to select the best one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I met.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were people from France, from Poland, from Italy, from Hungary, from operas, from philharmonia, from conservatoriums, and so on and so on, so very high professional, high professional, people, you know?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we enjoyed sometimes, it was about nine, 10 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For two hours, they played.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had-- we forgot completely about the camp, about-- of course, not all, but not all were interested, but most of us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was, before the kitchen, you know, there was a place of the orchestra close to the gate, entrance gate to the camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a plenty, with, with thousands of people there, sitting and watching and listening to this beautiful.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was, I would say, a visit from the outside world in the death camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then another story-- the SS, as you know, the German, are very keen in sport.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As we had couple of good boxers in the camp, even European champion, so they organized boxing between two them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, no one had a physical condition as he had before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even I remember a Polish boxer who was European champion fighting there, you know, with a Hungarian and this and that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was rather-- And then was in-- before the war, if you maybe remember, a very good team, soccer team, was a Hungarian team.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When the Hungarian Jews started to arrive, the, the German organize soccer teams to play.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they played.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a-- I, I remember still the name of a, of a referee.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
